Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.55,0:02:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}玻璃风景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道前路有什么而感到不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.30,0:02:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清前路的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有讨厌的事情也会努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩儿别想那些烦心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是阿一的监护人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别飚那么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是 监护人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.10,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八音盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里传来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不像是外面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收音机开着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.60,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,静养院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳驾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 劳驾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个八音盒声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}音乐是G弦上的咏叹调 作曲J.S.Bach
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看见的景色里也回响着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事早说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是一个人也没有的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转一圈就回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你看到的景色一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的风景是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是觉得有什么不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为某种原因才发出声音的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你叫妮娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 没有爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里挺安静啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的患者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.00,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生和护士们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起就没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们来做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这里有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.80,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 爸爸是这里的院长的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为正好到附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定顺便拜访一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是朝这边来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 眼睛的颜色好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头发也好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以摸一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好顺滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手怎么冷冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招呼打了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,院长今天可能外出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周末经常外出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,院长是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一会再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们住在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多空房间 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜会帮你们安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们在镇上预定了房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.10,0:09:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雾这么大 回不去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那孩子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登录了地狱通信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚才就到处瞄了几眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这房里似乎没有电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个静养院本身就很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 对什么怀着怨恨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再想了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去 阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等雾散了马上就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是偶然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫柴田的记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是依据事前到手的情报行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是为了什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.80,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许小姐本人也是无意识地在这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.40,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 最近小姐真让人搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.00,0:11:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没想到会接受这种委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自灵魂的访问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么迟 我都等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受你的委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法接受是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是会为我消除怨恨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的工作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨无法消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在的妮娜有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去泡茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫的爸爸真体贴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妮娜的爸爸是天壤之别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.20,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的爸爸扔下妮娜走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 可以问你点问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以不回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你登录了地狱通信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 连过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对谁心怀怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 对谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.70,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抛下我一个人好寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是爸爸不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经没关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小鸫在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有了新的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们永远和我在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会丢下妮娜一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.40,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 我们只是路过和院长打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么院长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里除了妮娜以外 什么人也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后我们三人一起好好生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是一家人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吗 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样跑到车子那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是小姐的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到变成救了那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们和这个委托没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 跟妮娜一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.00,0:17:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我发动啊这个破烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有消除妮娜的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没你的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不能把他们卷进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鸫他们不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要丢下妮娜一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像妮娜的爸爸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又让妮娜孤单一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是妮娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回忆下试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的景像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.70,0:21:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会等着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地等着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到我身边吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把妮娜的记忆
