Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.10,0:24:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.70,0:24:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上川美纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.70,0:24:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人每天都叫我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.40,0:24:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人只是为了仇恨而活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.40,0:24:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 那小家伙们就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.40,0:24:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿望是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.70,0:24:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她流放到地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.80,0:24:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
